data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Experience the beauty and tranquility of the backyard oasis, the elegance of the interior featuring Primary on the main, and the endless possibilities of a dream home brought to life. Take a dip in the dazzling salt-water pool on a scorching summer day, surrounded by a meticulously fenced-in yard that ensures your privacy. Lounge in the shaded gazebo and embrace the serenity of your surroundings. Marvel at the exquisite landscaped berm, adding a touch of natural beauty to the ambiance. As you step inside, you'll be immediately captivated by the undeniable charm and elegance. This gem offers a visual and emotional haven that is sure to captivate your heart. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite corner lot property your own.
